,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4324be2f3aaef38ff8392988c3f80d31184e0ed","tid":790273,"uid":113000,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"一開波講到穩賺咁依家已經講定蝕錢條數點填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"氹你落搭實話穩賺架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8495c64bfa1062fa9d9be4cba4ed0abd564ed5eb","tid":790273,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"我都分析過<br />\n香港大撚把車可以去深圳,又快又平<br />\n你人為停左呢類車無用,因為班友仔只會唔去大陸留港消費<br />\n高鐵票價對一般人太高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果去遠d不如機票"},{"pid":"8e8fbfd8ba42118258e90030f004d56350de31c2","tid":790273,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"紅van，客滿即開"},{"pid":"0991567d4eaa5a198ef3f8a1f82db4798c184714","tid":790273,"uid":9887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"東鐵三十幾蚊去福田<br />\n鳩鐵就要80蚊<br />\n雖則快幾個字，但係大部分人去東鐵沿線都近過鳩鐵好多，大西北嗰班都唔可能走去搭鳩鐵<br />\n結果得住尖咀佐敦西九班人可能會搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08f58e0990aba090862a07d436f981351b0efee","tid":790273,"uid":8040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e8fbfd8ba42118258e90030f004d56350de31c2","tid":790273,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"紅van，客滿即開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:52:23.000Z","msg":"呢個idea 正, 拎條隧道行紅Van<br />\n香港出境之後上19座紅Van, 時速130km/h 直飛福田, 入中國境之後搭鳩鐵/ 去飲喜茶<br />\n<br />\n咁樣短途線應該可以3分鐘一班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b763642dc392533202927318e2f3c3f18cc5de","tid":790273,"uid":2521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b517a48cac1d16598f9c0dcd3cfa88aca1890145","tid":790273,"uid":37586,"li